<paragraph blockId="24.[142,361,704,726]" box="[142,361,704,726]" pageId="24" pageNumber="51">
<emphasis box="[142,230,704,725]" italics="true" pageId="24" pageNumber="51">Female.</emphasis>
Unknown.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="24.[142,757,752,805]" pageId="24" pageNumber="51">
<emphasis box="[142,267,752,773]" italics="true" pageId="24" pageNumber="51">Etymology.</emphasis>
Refers to the absence of the arista in this species.
</paragraph>
